<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wedding Invitation</title>
    <style>
        /* Customize your invitation styles here */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f1e3; /* Light beige color */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .invitation-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .invitation-background {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: url('background_invitation.avif');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            filter: brightness(0.5); /* Adjust the brightness to your preference */
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #6d214f; /* Deep mauve color */
            font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive;
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .message {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #333; /* Dark grey color */
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .details {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6d214f; /* Deep mauve color */
        }
        .url {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #6d214f; /* Deep mauve color */
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666; /* Medium grey color */
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="invitation-container">
        <div class="invitation-background"></div>
        <h1>Formal Invitation</h1>
        <p class="message">Dear <%= guest %>,</p>
        <p class="message"><%= commonMessage %></p>
        <p class="message">We are delighted to invite you to celebrate our wedding with us.</p>
        <p class="message">Date: <span class="detail-label"><%= weddingDate %></span></p>
        <p class="message">Time: <span class="detail-label"><%= weddingTime %></span></p>
        <p class="message">Venue: <span class="detail-label"><%= venue %></span></p>
        <p class="message">Address: <span class="detail-label"><%= address %></span></p>
        <p class="message">We request the pleasure of your company on this joyous occasion.</p>
        <p class="message">Kindly join us as we begin our new journey together.</p>
        <p class="message">Watch the live event at:</p>
        <p class="url"><%= meetingLink %></p>
        <p class="footer">With warm regards,</p>
        <p class="footer"><%=inviterName%></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
